{
  "text": "In [CITATION_1] Formulas (4.5) and (4.9)], two vector-valued functions m(z) and m(z), depending on parameters s and \u03c4 , are introduced as the linear combinations of the columns of the solution to the tacnode RHP. By the relation (1.70) between the tacnode RHP and RHP 1.5, we have in our notations",
